description: This source file implements the platform-dependent setup manager creation function for the Sys Setup Manager Object in a BroadWay Runtime System Environment. It contains the function SysCreateSetupManager which calls SysSmoCreate to instantiate the setup manager object.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE SysCreateSetupManager(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates a new Sys Setup Manager Object by calling the SysSmoCreate function with provided container, owner, and reserved contexts.
